  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the diagnostic value of serum NT - proBNP in stroke
      associated with nonvalvular atrial fibrilltion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      All included in the cases in 7 days of blood samples, the detection of serum NT -
      proBNP.Through the single factor analysis to determine the serum NT - proBNP central source
      sex stroke prediction values.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
